anagers involved with day-to-day operations of a business. The correct answer is C. Transaction processing system.\"", "\"PASSWORD CONTROLS QUIZ\":\"This quiz asks which of the following would NOT be an effective control over the use of passwords. The correct answer is B. Keeping a written record of passwords.\""], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-3-small", "temperature": 0.0, "frequency_penalty": null, "presence_penalty": null, "top_p": 1.0, "max_tokens": 4000, "n": 1}}